    <ol>
      <li id="fn-1">
        Haynes RB, Wilczynski N, McKibbon KA, Walker CJ, Sinclair JC. Developing optimal search strategies for detecting clinically sound studies in MEDLINE. <em>J Am Med Inform Assoc</em> 1994;1(6):447–58.
        <a href="#fnref-1" class="footnote-back" aria-label="Voltar ao texto da nota 1">↩</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        Wilczynski NL, Haynes RB. EMBASE search strategies for identifying methodologically sound causation studies and for finding original articles on the diagnosis of common surgical conditions. <em>J Med Libr Assoc</em> 2007;95(1):85–7.
      </li>
      <li>
        BIREME / OPAS / OMS. <em>DeCS — Descritores em Ciências da Saúde</em>. Disponível em: <a href="https://decs.bvsalud.org" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">decs.bvsalud.org</a>.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </section>
</DocLayout>
